nitiative.ch/initiative-erklaert/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkonzern-initiative.ch%2Finitiative-erklaert%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=e05ba836\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://konzern-initiative.ch/initiative-erklaert/</a><br />\n<br />\n即使過到, 政府點加強措施又會討論一大輪, 分分鐘2,3年後先實施, 而瑞士企業在中國和香港的業務只係或受到影響<br />\n<br />\n咁當然如果條法例過到, 而又有人提告或瑞士政府借啲椅做野梗係好, 只係想大家了解真相同瑞士制度<br />\n______<br />\n上面個網頁就係公投嘅專頁, 有英文.<br />\n<br />\n你亦可直接係下面睇公投嘅法律全文兼解釋:<br />\n<a href=\"https://corporatejustice.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/KVI_Factsheet_5_E.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcorporatejustice.ch%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2FKVI_Factsheet_5_E.pdf&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=ea87fe27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://corporatejustice.ch/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/KVI_Factsheet_5_E.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"6e3399e7ec4aa101dc10bdd0c2aeb0c3bdaebef1","tid":2148712,"uid":268265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700eab8a9d2d00d8d5a7a741f729c95c1eae4e0c","tid":2148712,"uid":252064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"係「壹傳媒」<br />\n名好緊要<br />\n唔好打錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"指黎生被捕? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nzz.ch/international/hongkong-polizei-verhaftet-medienmogul-jimmy-lai-ld.1570493?reduced=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nzz.ch%2Finternational%2Fhongkong-polizei-verhaftet-medienmogul-jimmy-lai-ld.1570493%3Freduced%3Dtrue&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9e4cadde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nzz.ch/international/hongkong-polizei-verhaftet-medienmogul-jimmy-lai-ld.1570493?reduced=true</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.watson.ch/international/china/116381787-hongkong-kritischer-verleger-jimmy-lai-festgenommen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watson.ch%2Finter